description: Boxes and crates are piled on top of each other, cluttering the small room.  Nestled into the northern wall is a bent iron cage housing a multi-horned tusked rolton.  A fierce smell emits from the rolton's cage.  A large sign hanging over the cage reads, "Wolton bites!  Eats fingurs."
title: [The Goblin Oddity, The Rolton]
